 deg til Trondheims svar p\u00e5 Victoria Beckham, lover R\u00f8skaft.", "\u2013 \u00c5 ja, gj\u00f8r det! Julaften! H\u00f8rer du Erik, n\u00e5 m\u00e5 du begynne \u00e5 tjene mer penger enn David Beckham, for n\u00e5 blir jeg snart Victoria, str\u00e5ler Simonsen.", "Og om noen timer skal hun og samboeren Erik feire jul for f\u00f8rste gang i felles hjem."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "044e7168f2e499f2abb07e0de8064a8e707877dd12d56c055d084e9ecc36a8d0"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-11-17T18:02:11.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Ved vasken st\u00e5r Gilde-mekaniker Stig Roar Hoff. I stolen sitter Einar Woldseth. \u2013 Det er f\u00f8rste gangen en mekaniker har vasket h\u00e5ret mitt p\u00e5 julaften. Men det funker, flirer Woldseth."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1283336.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/juleklipp%20001"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/5970822c0b53e211b631e13c227dbf82b0c5f8dd.jpg?598acfa1"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Fikk gratis klipp p\u00e5 julaften -adressa.no", "Fullt hus", "Min mekanikerfris\u00f8r", "Victoria og David"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "5970822c0b53e211b631e13c227dbf82b0c5f8dd"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "style-and-fashion"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["vaske h\u00e5r", "gratis klipp", "h\u00e5r", "vaske", "fris\u00f8r", "julaften"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["erik", "stars 